title: The Parlor Game
description: Principal Conklin is not happy when Walter Denton takes a romantic interest in his daughter.

title: A Dry Scalp Is Better Than None
description: When hypochondriac Angela lies that her doctor's given her a month to live, Miss Brooks, Mr. Boynton and Mr. Conklin throw her a last Christmas party, all dressed in Santa Claus costumes.

title: Just Remember the Red River Valley
Le chien chaud et le mouton noir
The Big Jump
description: Principal Osgood agrees to jump from the top of the high school into a fireman's net as a publicity stunt, but gets cold feet as the hour for his leap nears. He fakes an injury, then tries to convince the male teachers to take his place. When they all develop mysterious maladies, it's up to Miss Brooks to uphold the faculty's honor.

title: Top Hat, White Tie, and Bridle
